metadata.title: 3M Durapore Cloth Tape, Non Sterile, White, 2" x 10 Yds, 6 Per Box, Secure Dressings and Equipment
features: High strength, versatile, conformable Durapore Cloth Tape
Box of 6 Rolls, 2" x 10 yd (5 cm x 9.14 m)
"Silk-like" cloth tape with strong adhesion works well for many different applications, such as securing bulky dressings, heavier tubing, and small splints
Convenient bidirectional tear makes it easy and quick to use without scissors.
Hypoallergenic and not made with natural rubber latex
description: High strength tape comes as a box of six rolls. Each roll measures 2" x 10 yd.
